snippet.title: Parenthood 5x06 Promo "The M Word" (HD)
snippet.description:
Parenthood 5x06 "The M Word" - Sarah (Lauren Graham) and Amber (Mae Whitman) struggle with the wedding bell blues while Julia (Erika Christensen) and Joel (Sam Jaeger) try to keep it all together. Kristina (Monica Potter) and Adam (Peter Krause) hit the campaign trail hard and enlist Team Braverman to go door-to-door, while Jasmine (Joy Bryant) helps usher in a new era for Crosby (Dax Shepard) and his band on the run. Zeek (Craig T. Nelson) gives Camille (Bonnie Bedelia) a little of what she wants. Also starring Max Burkholder, Miles Heizer, Matt Lauria, Savannah Paige Rae, Xolo Mariduena. Guest starring, David Denman, Jurnee Smollett. Subscribe to tvpromosdb on YouTube for more Parenthood season 5 promos in HD!
